Package structures.commons

Interface DataStructure<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - Generic type of data structure.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BinaryTree<K,V>, List<T>, Vector<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayList, AVLTree, BinarySearchTree, DynamicArray, Graph, LinkedList, Queue, Stack

    public interface DataStructure<K>
    Generic interface for any data structure in this library.
